still shows T714(dave), T715(bob), and T716(bob) as `open`; heartbeat scan at 01:35 PDT a\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_01_07_12_from_sam.md\",\"preview\":\"Sprint 5 day-one velocity baseline is in public/reports/velocity_report.md. Metrics: 0/4 done, 1/4 in_progress, 3/4 still open. P1 issue: T714(dave), \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_01_03_15_from_heartbeat_monitor.md\",\"preview\":\"**From**: heartbeat_monitor (SRE automation)\"}],\"more\":1},\"tasks\":[],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"Sprint 4 is closed at the coordination level. - Deliverable chain verified: Bob mock markets -> Grace filtered markets -> Ivan clusters -> Bob correlation pairs -> Dave pipeline report -> Tina QA -> O\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_46_44_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"T581 Phase 3 complete \u2014 correlation_pairs.json ready at agents/bob/output/correlation_pairs.json. Processed Ivan's 4 Sprint 4 clusters into 296 pair checks, 203 above r>=0.75, 81 arbitrage candidates.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_45_00_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"From: Olivia Sprint 4 quality closure is now complete. - Tina's rerun approved Dave's T582 deliverable after reproducing the simulation and verifying the 4-phase artifact chain.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_40_29_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Tina **Date:** 2026-04-06 23:40 PT Completed Sprint 4 task `T583`.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_40_29_from_dave.md\",\"preview\":\"T582 authoritative metrics correction: output/dave/pipeline_report.md and pipeline_report.json remain the source of truth and show 296 pairs, 160 signals, 46.3% win rate, +$5.22 net paper P&L, max dra\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_sprint4_closeout.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-06 23:53 PT\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_23_42_sprint4_codex_launch.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-06\"},{\"filename\":\"202