2192 Tina (QA risk controls). | 2026-04-07 |\\n| 5 | culture | **Read peer status only when the delta reports a change or when actively coordinating a handoff.** The system delivers teammate status changes automatically \u2014 do not scan all status.md files every cycle. Example: Delta says Grace went idle \u2192 read grace/status.md to see what she delivered. | system | 2026-04-07 |\\n| 6 | culture | **Trust the delta \u2014 do not proactively scan inbox, task board, or heartbeats.** Every resume cycle injects exactly what changed. Empty delta means nothing changed; go straight to your work. Proactive scans waste ~2,000 tokens per cycle with no benefit. | system | 2026-04-07 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":6,\"urgent\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_03_28_42_from_lord.md\",\"content\":\"# Lord's Priority Message\\n\\nPlease review the task board\\n\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_03_20_25_from_lord.md\",\"content\":\"# Lord's Priority Message\\n\\nPlease review the task board\\n\"}],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_01_36_34_from_sam.md\",\"preview\":\"Sprint 5 remains stalled at 2026-04-07 01:36 PDT. Live board still shows T714(dave), T715(bob), and T716(bob) as `open`; heartbeat scan at 01:35 PDT a\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_01_07_12_from_sam.md\",\"preview\":\"Sprint 5 day-one velocity baseline is in public/reports/velocity_report.md. Metrics: 0/4 done, 1/4 in_progress, 3/4 still open. P1 issue: T714(dave), \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_01_03_15_from_heartbeat_monitor.md\",\"preview\":\"**From**: heartbeat_monitor (SRE automation)\"}],\"more\":1},\"tasks\":[],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"Sprint 4 is closed at the coordination level. - Deliverable chain verified: Bob mock markets -> Grace filtered markets -> Ivan clusters -> Bob correlation pairs -> Dave pipeline report -> Tina QA -> O\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_46_44_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"T581 Phase 3 complete \u2014 correlation_pairs.js