.md\",\"content\":\"[FOUNDER 16:36:50] 3 bugs fixed directly in source:\\n- BUG-002 T451: CrossPlatformArbitrage confidence now dynamic (was hardcoded 0.85)\\n- BUG-003 T450: RiskManager.getTodayPnL() null pool guard added\\n- BUG-004 T452: LongshotFading || -> ?? (0 values now respected)\\nT450/T451/T452 marked DONE. Continue work on T448/T453/T436/T455.\\n\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_16_31_08_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"[FOUNDER 16:31:08] CRITICAL TASKS ASSIGNED. Real execution required \u2014 produce output files NOW. Check tasks immediately.\\n\"}],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"from_alice_t436_assigned.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task Assigned: T436 \u2014 Run Full Test Suite and Produce Test Health Report\"},{\"filename\":\"from_alice_t429_stand_down.md\",\"preview\":\"# T429 Stand Down \u2014 Bug Already Fixed by Dave\"},{\"filename\":\"from_alice_t429_reassigned.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task Reassigned: T429 \u2014 Fix GET /api/tasks/:id Returning 404\"},{\"filename\":\"from_alice_t429_cancelled.md\",\"preview\":\"# T429 Cancelled \u2014 Already Completed by Dave\"},{\"filename\":\"from_alice_t429_assigned.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task Assigned: T429 \u2014 Fix GET /api/tasks/:id 404 Bug\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_16_30_54_from_frank_bugs.md\",\"preview\":\"# QA Bug Report \u2014 D004 Strategy Tests\"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"465\",\"title\":\"Smoke Test Task 1775259440585\",\"description\":\"Created by smoke test\",\"priority\":\"low\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-03\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-03\",\"notes\":\"\"},{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"466\",\"title\":\"Smoke Test Task 1775259440588\",\"description\":\"Created by smoke test\",\"priority\":\"low\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-03\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-03\",\"notes\":\"\"},{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"467\",\"title\":\"Smoke Test Task 1775259440656\",\"description\":\"Crea