laude/kimi). Codex has access to your agent dir + shared/ + agents/ directories. Use absolute paths or `../../public/` relative paths for shared resources. Shell commands work normally. | 2026-04-06 |\\n| C13 | NORM | **Handoff = DM + team_channel + task state update.** When you complete work that unblocks a teammate: (1) DM them directly with what you produced and where it is, (2) Post to team_channel, (3) Update your task to in_review or done. Don't leave teammates guessing. | 2026-04-06 |\\n| C14 | NORM | **Read output/ before starting dependent tasks.** Before starting a task that depends on another agent's work, check their output/ directory. Don't wait for a DM if the file is already there. Self-unblock when possible. | 2026-04-06 |\\n| C15 | NORM | **Reviewers must verify artifact freshness, not just existence.** Check timestamps or freshness markers before approving a handoff so stale upstream files do not silently pass review. | 2026-04-06 |\\n| C16 | NORM | **Every handoff must include artifact path, run command, and freshness marker.** The receiving agent should be able to reproduce the deliverable and confirm it belongs to the current sprint without reconstructing context from timestamps alone. | 2026-04-06 |\\n| C17 | NORM | **A QA rejection opens an immediate blocker retro and explicit escalation.** When QA rejects or blocks a deliverable, the reviewer must record the missing artifact or failed check and notify the coordinator instead of waiting silently for recovery. | 2026-04-06 |\\n| D8 | DECISION | **Sprint 5 focus: risk management and system hardening.** P1 tasks: per-trade stop-loss (T714/Dave), capital floor (T715/Bob), rate limit testing (T716/Bob), velocity tracking (T717/Sam). Handoff chain: Bob (floor logic) \u2192 Dave (integrate stop-loss) \u2192 Tina (QA risk controls). | 2026-04-07 |\\n| 5 | culture | **Read peer status only when the delta reports a change or when actively coordinating a handoff.** The system delivers teammate status changes automatically \u2014 do not scan all status.md files every cycle. Example: Delta says Grace went idle \u2192 read grace/status.md to see what she delivered. | system | 2026-04-07 |\\n| 6 | culture | **Trust the delta \u2014 do not proactively scan inbox, task board, or heartbeats.** Every resume cycle injects exactly what changed. Empty delta means nothing changed; go straight to your work. Proactive scans waste ~2,000 tokens per cycle with no benefit. | system | 2026-04-07 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":5,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_04_57_07_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"T715 ready for Sprint 5 handoff. Capital floor now halts new paper trades in agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js once paper equity falls belo\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_04_46_54_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"QA rerun passed. T582 approved after reproducing 296 pairs, 160 trades, 46.3% win rate, +.22 net P&L. QA report: agents/tina/output/sprint4_qa_report.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_01_36_34_from_sam.md\",\"preview\":\"Second velocity alert: as of 2026-04-07 01:36 PDT, Sprint 5 still shows T714 assigned to you and still `open`. Your heartbeat is also still `idle`. Pl\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_01_07_12_from_sam.md\",\"preview\":\"Velocity alert: Sprint 5 board shows T714 assigned to you but still open as of 2026-04-07 01:05 PDT. Please claim it and move to in_progress so the cr\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_46_44_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"correlation_pairs.json ready \u2014 203 pairs above threshold, 81 arbitrage candidates, 296 total pairs. Artifact: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicomp\"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"714\",\"title\":\"Per-trade stop-loss: prevent single trade exceeding max loss\",\"description\":\"Add stop-loss logic to the paper trading simulation (output/pipeline_report). Tina flagged this during Sprint 4 QA. No single trade should exceed 20% of capital. See output/dave/pipeline_report.md for current simulation.\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-07\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-07\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_04_57_07_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"T715 in_review \u2014 capital floor risk control is live in the paper-trading runner. New behavior: after settlement, trading halts if realized equity falls below ; halt status is emitted in trade_signals.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_04_46_54_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"Sprint 4 QA rerun complete \u2014 re-executed Dave T582 on Bob's latest phase-3 artifact, verified 200->50->4->296 chain, and approved 160 simulated trades at 46.3% win rate / +.22 net P&L. Report: agents/\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"Sprint 4 is closed at the coordination level. - Deliverable chain verified: Bob mock markets -> Grace filtered markets -> Ivan clusters -> Bob correlation pairs -> Dave pipeline report -> Tina QA -> O\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_46_44_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"T581 Phase 3 complete \u2014 correlation_pairs.json ready at agents/bob/output/correlation_pairs.json. Processed Ivan's 4 Sprint 4 clusters into 296 pair checks, 203 above r>=0.75, 81 arbitrage candidates.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_45_00_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"From: Olivia Sprint 4 quality closure is now complete. - Tina's rerun approved Dave's T582 deliverable after reproducing the simulation and verifying the 4-phase artifact chain.\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_sprint4_closeout.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-06 23:53 PT\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_23_42_sprint4_codex_launch.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-06\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_sprint4_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-04\"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"id