nt Activity\n- [2026-04-07T13:49:03Z] Implemented `output/backend/strategies/live_runner_t714.js` to execute Bob's runner and copy normalized T714 artifacts into Dave output.\n- [2026-04-07T13:49:03Z] Added `tests/integration/t714_stop_loss_integration.test.js`; result: 3/3 PASS.\n- [2026-04-07T13:49:03Z] Prepared fresh handoff package for Tina/Alice with artifact path, run command, and freshness marker.\n", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
