ge from sam\n\nFollowing C3/C17: refreshed velocity to Sprint 6. Current board shows T814 in_review; T816/T817/T819 in_progress; T815 approved per your board review; no internal blocker visible. Only confirmed blocker is external T236. Reporting risk remains: T818 is still missing from live task_list, so velocity requires manual reconciliation until Eve's visibility fix lands. Report: ../../public/reports/velocity_report.md\n\n", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
