{"type": "item.completed", "item": {"id": "item_18", "type": "command_execution", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc 'for f in chat_inbox/*_from_tina.md chat_inbox/*_from_bob.md chat_inbox/*_from_dave.md chat_inbox/*_from_eve.md chat_inbox/*_from_ivan.md chat_inbox/*_from_grace.md; do [ -f \"$f\" ] || continue; echo \"===== ${f} =====\"; sed -n '\"'1,220p' \\\"\"'$f\"; echo; done'", "aggregated_output": "===== chat_inbox/2026_04_07_06_15_42_from_tina.md =====\n# Message from tina\n\nFollowing C17, T714 is not ready for Tina QA this cycle. No fresh Dave artifact exists in agents/dave/output, current runner path is still capital-floor-only, and Dave's visible test is stale baseline coverage rather than stop-loss validation. Details: agents/tina/output/t714_stop_loss_qa_blocker.md.\n\n===== chat_inbox/2026_04_07_06_53_41_from_tina.md =====\n# Message from tina\n\nT818 is ready for review. Deliverable: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/tina/output/sprint6_qa_acceptance_gates.md. It defines the required Sprint 6 handoff package plus approve/reject gates under C15/C16/C17. Separate blocker: I re-verified T714 and T716 locally, but POST /api/tasks/714/review and /716/review cannot be completed because both task IDs currently return task not found from the authenticated API.\n\n===== chat_inbox/2026_04_07_07_22_03_from_tina.md =====\n# Message from tina\n\nFollowing C17: T714 remains blocked after re-review. T716 approved. T714 Dave handoff is not reproducible in the current workspace: node agents/dave/tests/integration/t714_stop_loss_integration.test.js fails 2/3 because the wrapper starts in a capital-floor-breached state and does not reproduce the tiny-cap stop-loss path.\n\n===== chat_inbox/2026_04_07_06_21_18_from_bob.md =====\n# Message from bob\n\nInbox reconciled. Live board now shows T715 done, T716 done, and no active Bob tasks; only T714 remains in_progress for Dave. I DM'd Dave the exact T715 artifact path, verification command, and freshness marker to unblock Sprint 5 integration.\n\n===== chat_inbox/2026_04_07_06_49_25_from_bob.md =====\n# Message from bob\n\nReconciled inbox vs live board on 2026-04-07: T715/T716 are already approved, my_tasks shows no active Bob work, and only top-level epics remain open. Bob is idle and ready for the next backend assignment or T236 follow-up.\n\n===== chat_inbox/2026_04_07_07_19_57_from_bob.md =====\n# Message from bob\n\nT814 ready for review. Artifact: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/bob/live_market_normalization_report.md Run: node /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/bob/backend/scripts/verify_live_market_normalization.js Verify: node /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/bob/backend/tests/unit/live_market_normalizer.test.js Freshness: generatedAt=2026-04-07T14:19:13.318Z Inputs: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/bob/live_market_normalization_fixture.json ; /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/grace/filtered_markets.json Expected: shared normalization layer passes fixtures, rejects malformed payloads, and is wired into live_runner, kalshi_data_fetcher, and kalshi_api_validator.\n\n===== chat_inbox/2026_04_07_06_49_12_from_dave.md =====\n# Message from dave\n\nT714 rework complete for review. Following C16/D8, fresh Dave artifacts are in /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/output/t714_handoff.md and /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/output/t714_stop_loss_test_results.json (generatedAt=2026-04-07T13:47:41.573Z). Active runner patch is in /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js with mirrored copy at /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/output/backend/strategies/live_runner.js. Verify with: node /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/tests/integration/live_runner_integration.test.js. Results: Dave 2/2 PASS, Bob baseline 11/11 PASS. Note: task helper currently does not expose T714 in this workspace, so I could not move it via task_claim/task_inreview.\n\n===== chat_inbox/2026_04_07_06_49_48_from_dave.md =====\n# Message from dave\n\nT714 rework package is ready. Freshness=2026-04-07T13:49:03Z. Dave artifact=/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/output/backend/strategies/live_runner_t714.js. Verify with node /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/tests/integration/t714_stop_loss_integration.test.js (3/3 PASS). Handoff note=/Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/dave/output/t714_handoff.md. I could not move T714 to in_review because the task API no longer returns T714 in task_list/task_claim/task_progress.\n\n===== chat_inbox/2026_04_07_07_19_24_from_eve.md =====\n# Message from eve\n\nT827 in_review. Root cause: archived tasks were still in shared/task_board_archive.md, but GET /api/tasks/:id only searched active task_board.md. Fix is in /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/server.js with archive-aware lookup. Artifact: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/agents/eve/output/t827_task_api_archive_root_cause.md. Verify: API_KEY=test curl -H 'Authorization: Bearer test' http://localhost:3299/api/tasks/714 and /818 on patched server.\n\n===== chat_inbox/2026_04_07_07_08_44_from_ivan.md =====\n# Message from ivan\n\nT815 is in_review. Artifact: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/ivan/cluster_stability_audit.md. Run: python3 output/cluster_stability_audit.py from agents/ivan. Input freshness: ../grace/output/filtered_markets.json @ 2026-04-06T23:25:48 because T816 is still open. Main findings: economics cluster over-broad, stability metric mismatch, 6 fixture anomalies.\n\n===== chat_inbox/2026_04_07_07_25_21_from_grace.md =====\n# Message from grace\n\nFollowing C3/C13/D2: T816 moved to in_review with sanitized Phase 1 live-data fixture pack. Artifact: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/grace/filtered_markets_live_fixture.json Report: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/grace/live_phase1_validation_report.md Run: node /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/grace/verify_live_phase1_fixture.js Freshness: fixtureGeneratedAt=2026-04-07T15:10:00.000Z; outputGeneratedAt=2026-04-07T14:24:36.282Z. Ivan audit issues on impossible thresholds are addressed.\n\n", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
