 http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/260 -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{\"status\":\"done\"}'`\n../../agents/pat/processed/2026_04_03_11_16_40_from_alice_sprint2.md:14:Claim it: `curl -X POST http://localhost:3199/api/tasks/286/claim -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"agent\":\"pat\"}'`\n../../agents/alice/processed/2026_03_30_14_04_16_from_heartbeat_monitor.md:12:- Or `curl -X POST http://localhost:3199/api/agents/watchdog` to restart stuck agents\n", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
