 |\n|------|--------------|------------------|---------------|--------------|\n| bob | 552 | 487 | 65 | 33 |\n| alice | 525 | 428 | 95 | 37 |\n| dave | 491 | 430 | 60 | 38 |\n| olivia | 352 | 341 | 10 | 22 |\n| tina | 351 | 340 | 11 | 28 |\n| sam | 159 | 152 | 6 | 17 |\n| grace | 158 | 148 | 10 | 27 |\n| ivan | 158 | 148 | 9 | 28 |\n\n## Per-Agent Metrics\n\n| Agent | Today Cycles | Completed Cycles | Active Cycles | Action Count | Latest Cycle |\n|------|--------------|------------------|---------------|--------------|--------------|\n| alice | 525 | 428 | 95 | 37 | 523 |\n| bob | 552 | 487 | 65 | 33 | 552 |\n| charlie | 137 | 118 | 18 | 31 | 136 |\n| dave | 491 | 430 | 60 | 38 | 490 |\n| eve | 108 | 98 | 10 | 29 | 108 |\n| frank | 66 | 59 | 7 | 20 | 66 |\n| grace | 158 | 148 | 10 | 27 | 158 |\n| heidi | 52 | 51 | 1 | 9 | 52 |\n| ivan | 158 | 148 | 9 | 28 | 157 |\n| judy | 54 | 54 | 0 | 6 | 54 |\n| karl | 54 | 53 | 1 | 6 | 54 |\n| liam | 60 | 59 | 1 | 6 | 60 |\n| mia | 55 | 53 | 2 | 7 | 55 |\n| nick | 55 | 53 | 2 | 5 | 55 |\n| olivia | 352 | 341 | 10 | 22 | 351 |\n| pat | 57 | 57 | 0 | 6 | 57 |\n| quinn | 55 | 55 | 0 | 3 | 55 |\n| rosa | 59 | 58 | 1 | 4 | 59 |\n| sam | 159 | 152 | 6 | 17 | 158 |\n| tina | 351 | 340 | 11 | 28 | 351 |\n\n## Method\n\n- Task state source: live `task_board.md` plus archived Sprint 6 closure records for `T814`-`T819`\n- Cycle source: `/api/agents/*/cycles`\n- Cost source: `/api/cost`\n", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
