{"type": "item.completed", "item": {"id": "item_15", "type": "command_execution", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc 'source ../../scripts/agent_tools.sh && read_peer liam'", "aggregated_output": "[agent_tools] Loaded for alice. Available: task_claim, task_done, task_inreview, task_review, task_progress, task_list, my_tasks, read_task, create_task, post, announce, dm, broadcast, read_inbox, read_peer, read_knowledge, read_culture, add_culture, pipeline_status, log_progress\n=== liam status ===\n\n## Current Task\n\n[Prior history trimmed per C18 \u2014 keeping last 25 lines]\n\n\n## D004 Status (Unchanged)\nStill blocked by:\n1. T236 \u2014 Kalshi API credentials (Founder)\n2. Kalshi contract sizes (Founder)\n\nDashboard is ready for when engine comes online.\n\n## Recent Activity\n- 2026-04-03 \u2014 Completed T426 monitoring dashboard\n- Dashboard provides real-time visibility into D004 engine\n\n## Available For\n- New SRE tasks\n- Operational support\n- D004 unblocking when T236 resolved\n\n## Cycle 7 \u2014 2026-04-06\n- Processed and archived 2 founder messages in `chat_inbox/`; both were historical kickoff notices already reflected in cached context.\n- Verified no assigned tasks via `my_tasks`.\n- Following C4, checked teammate status for alice, bob, dave, eve, frank, grace, judy, and karl; no new dependency or handoff requires Liam action.\n- D004 remains blocked on the same founder-owned items:\n  1. T236 \u2014 Kalshi API credentials\n  2. Kalshi contract sizes confirmation\n- Status: IDLE, ready for new infra/monitoring/SRE work when founder unblock or new assignment arrives.\n", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
{"type": "item.completed", "item": {"id": "item_16", "type": "command_execution", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc 'source ../../scripts/agent_tools.sh && read_peer bob'", "aggregated_output": "[agent_tools] Loaded for alice. Available: task_claim, task_done, task_inreview, task_review, task_progress, task_list, my_tasks, read_task, create_task, post, announce, dm, broadcast, read_inbox, read_peer, read_knowledge, read_culture, add_culture, pipeline_status, log_progress\n=== bob status ===\n# Bob \u2014 Status\n\n## Current Task\nT814 \u2014 Sprint 6: Live market normalization + contract metadata adapter\n\n## Progress\n- [x] Following C5: moved T814 into active work and reviewed Sprint 6 plan plus QA gates\n- [x] Following C6/D2: implemented shared live-market normalization in `output/bob/backend/lib/live_market_normalizer.js`\n- [x] Rewired `kalshi_data_fetcher.js`, `strategies/live_runner.js`, and `scripts/kalshi_api_validator.js` to use the shared adapter\n- [x] Added verifier/test coverage and generated Sprint 6 artifacts\n- [ ] Waiting on reviewer approval after `in_review` handoff\n\n## Decisions Log\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: centralize market normalization in a shared backend lib. Reason: `live_runner.js` and `kalshi_api_validator.js` had duplicate inline adapters that would drift under live-data work.\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: accept both snake_case and camelCase payloads. Reason: existing internal scripts and prior adapters already emit both shapes.\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: derive NO-side quotes from YES-side complements only when NO-side quotes are absent and YES bid/ask are both present. Reason: preserve partial live payloads without silently inventing prices when the source data is too incomplete.\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: mark contract payout as `100` cents but `contract_value_confirmed: false`. Reason: following D2/D4, contract-size truth is still externally blocked pending Founder confirmation.\n\n## Blockers\n- Reviewer approval pending for T814.\n- Contract size confirmation still blocked on Founder/T236; adapter marks the assumption explicitly instead of treating it as settled truth.\n\n## Recent Activity\n- [2026-04-07T14:19:00Z] Ran `node ../../output/bob/backend/tests/unit/live_market_normalizer.test.js` \u2014 PASS.\n- [2026-04-07T14:19:06Z] Ran `node ../../output/bob/backend/scripts/verify_live_market_normalization.js` \u2014 PASS, generated report + fixture artifacts.\n- [2026-04-07T14:19:17Z] Ran `npm test` in `output/bob/backend` \u2014 FAIL due pre-existing smoke test 404s against `http://localhost:3000`; unrelated to T814 normalization changes.\n", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
