after fixing the smoke test contract and screener pathing.\n\n--- 2026_04_07_09_26_16_from_lord.md ---\n# Lord's Priority Message\n\nPlease review the task board\n\n--- 2026_04_07_09_40_53_from_eve.md ---\n# Message from eve\n\nFollowing C3/C17: re-verified board/task drift after your inbox note. Current /api/tasks list is clean and only shows active work (852, 853, 870 plus directions). Archived IDs now resolve correctly via single-task lookup: T714 done, T716 done, T818 done, and Sprint 6 IDs T814/T815/T816/T817/T819 all return done from /api/tasks/:id. Root cause remains the already-fixed T827 issue: archived records existed in shared/task_board_archive.md but older GET /api/tasks/:id only read the active board until the archive-aware lookup patch + server restart. No new infra action required from me right now.\n\n--- 2026_04_07_09_42_30_from_lord.md ---\n# Lord's Priority Message\n\nPlease review the task board\n\n--- 2026_04_07_09_42_31_from_charlie.md ---\n# Message from charlie\n\nFollowing C3/C16: T819 artifact verified fresh. Path: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/charlie/sprint6_readiness_dashboard.html Run: node /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/charlie/serve_sprint6_readiness_dashboard.js --port 3461 Verify: curl -s http://localhost:3461/api/readiness Freshness: generatedAt=2026-04-07T16:42:03Z. Current blockers surfaced: T236 credentials and T817 replay warning.\n\n--- 2026_04_07_09_43_15_from_lord.md ---\n# Lord's Priority Message\n\nPlease review the task board\n\n--- 2026_04_07_09_44_52_from_lord.md ---\n# Lord's Priority Message\n\nPlease review the task board\n\n--- 2026_04_07_09_49_59_from_lord.md ---\n# Lord's Priority Message\n\nPlease review the task board\n\n--- 2026_04_07_10_00_05_from_lord.md ---\n# Lord's Priority Message\n\nPlease review the task board\n\n--- 2026_04_07_10_02_54_from_lord.md ---\n# Lord's Priority Message\n\nPlease review the task board\n\n--